<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400&family=Inter:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <title>Vic-falls Rafting Adventures</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007BFF;
        }
        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin: 0 15px;
        }
        .color-palette {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .color-box {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px black;
        }
        .color-code {
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Vic-falls Rafting Adventures</h1>
        <img src="wwr/images/zambezi.jpg" alt="Join our expert guides for an exhilarating journey down the rivers!" width="400" loading="lazy">
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="wwr/about.html">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#trips">Trips</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="home">
            <h2>Welcome to Vic-falls Rafting!</h2>
            <section id="hero">
                <img src="wwr/images/aaa.jpg" alt="Exciting rafting adventure" loading="lazy">
                <h2>Join the Adventure!</h2>
                <button onclick="location.href='#contact'">Book Your Trip Now!</button>
            </section>

            <section id="testimonials">
                <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
                <blockquote>"An unforgettable experience! Highly recommend!" - Evis mat</blockquote>
                <blockquote>"The guides were amazing and made us feel safe!" - ACH hj</blockquote>
            </section>

            <section id="about">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <img src="wwr/images/zim.jpg" alt="Enjoy rafting with us in Zambezi valley" width="500" loading="lazy">
                <p>We are passionate about providing safe and thrilling rafting experiences.</p>
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>At Vic-falls Rafting, we aim to provide unforgettable rafting experiences while prioritizing safety and environmental stewardship.</p>
                <h3>Our Story</h3>
                <p>Founded in 1998, our journey began with a passion for adventure and the great outdoors. Over the years, we have grown into a trusted name in rafting.</p>
                <h3>Meet Our Team</h3>
                <p>Our experienced guides are not only skilled in rafting but also passionate about sharing their love for nature.</p>
                <h3>Safety First</h3>
                <p>We adhere to the highest safety standards to ensure that your adventure is both thrilling and secure.</p>
                <h3>Join Us</h3>
                <p>Ready for your next adventure? Contact us at +263 782 641220 or email <a href="mailto:smatenda98@hotmail.com">smatenda98@hotmail.com</a> to book your rafting experience today!</p>
            </section>

            <section id="featured-trips">
                <h2>Featured Trips</h2>
                <div class="trip">
                    <h3>White Water Rafting</h3>
                    <p>Experience the thrill of Class V rapids!</p>
                    <button>Learn More</button>
                </div>
            </section>

            <p>Experience the thrill of navigating the rivers with our expert guides.</p>
            <button onclick="location.href='#contact'">Book Your Adventure</button>
        </section>

        <section id="trips">
            <h2>Our Trips</h2>
            <p>Explore our wide range of rafting adventures suitable for all skill levels.</p>
            <h3>Types of Trips</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Family-Friendly Adventures:</strong> Perfect for kids and beginners.</li>
                <li><strong>Extreme Thrills:</strong> For those seeking adrenaline-pumping rapids.</li>
                <li><strong>Scenic Floats:</strong> Enjoy a leisurely day on the water surrounded by nature.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Itinerary</h3>
            <p><strong>Sample Day:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>9:00 AM:</strong> Meet at the base camp</li>
                <li><strong>10:00 AM:</strong> Safety briefing and gear fitting</li>
                <li><strong>11:00 AM:</strong> Hit the water for an exciting rafting experience!</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Pricing</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Half-Day Trip:</strong> $65 per person + lunch</li>
                <li><strong>Full-Day Trip:</strong> $140 per person + dinner</li>
                <li><strong>Group Discounts Available!</strong></li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>For bookings, email <a href="mailto:smatenda98@hotmail.com">smatenda98@hotmail.com</a></p>
            <p>Complaints desk email: <a href="mailto:evismate98@gmail.com">evismate98@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p>Simply call: +263 782 641220</p>
            <p>Address: 12 Jacaranda Crescent, Victoria Falls</p>
            <form>
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                
                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
                
                <button type="submit">Send</button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Color Palette for Whitewater Rafting Site</h2>
            <div class="color-palette">
                <div class="color-box" style="background-color: #2cfd3d;">
                    <span>Primary</span>
                    <div class="color-code">#2cfd3d</div>
                </div>
                <div class="color-box" style="background-color: #512eff;">
                    <span>Secondary</span>
                    <div class="color-code">#512eff</div>
                </div>
                <div class="color-box" style="background-color: #fe2226;">
                    <span>Accent 1</span>
                    <div class="color-code">#fe2226</div>
                </div>
                <div class="color-box" style="background-color: #fe1eef;">
                    <span>Accent 2</span>
                    <div class="color-code">#fe1eef</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Vic-falls Rafting Adventures. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
